{
  "stem": "17761.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 157.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then later, we had already some medications possible to be-- to have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By bribing officers-- well, all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were doctors who had them, some that they brought with them, some-- so there was a little bit of possibility to help out people who became sick.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it depended very much what kind of a heart you had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the heart-- the strength of the heart that determined if you survived or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those who were sick and survived, they were immunized-- immunized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they could treat other people with-- with typhus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, we tried not to get mixed with such people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somehow, I treated a lot of people with typhus, and I-- I-- I thought I am completely immunized of that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it wasn't true because in-- at the end of 1942, I fell sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember the doctor coming to my father saying, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's Don't worry, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Rand, your son has a heart like a horse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And here I am.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then there was two other kind of typhus, which was called bowel typhus also abdomen typhus, and a [INAUDIBLE] typhus.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were-- these were propagated not by lice but by sanitary conditions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And many people died of that also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a big market.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At-- most the food we got by trading things that we brought with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You gave him a shirt, you got the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You get potatoes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You got all kinds of things like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We developed there a special culinary book for-- that was no book-- how to make-- how to eat something from-- from nothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
